===Noun===
'''sofa''' (plural: [[sofas]])

# An upholstered seat, typically having sides and back, long enough to accommodate two or more people.

===Etymology===
Derived from Arabic ''suffa'' (carpet or divan) from Aramaic ''sippa'', absolute form of ''sippeta'', or mat.  The word may have entered European languages due to the Moorish occupation of Spain.

